Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.04,0:00:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑟爾蓋先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平安無事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你突然就走了 我一直很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.93,0:00:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑟爾蓋先生才是沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格魯德曼的軟禁也就只能到潘德拉古為止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.41,0:00:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再就不能讓他隨心所欲了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.37,0:00:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅蘭斯皇帝 德蘭陛下的宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.79,0:00:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅蘭斯皇帝…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 這裡格魯德曼和青嵐騎士團都無法進入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德蘭陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.81,0:00:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是導師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我是導師史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝你遠道而來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.05,0:00:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朕是羅蘭斯皇帝 德蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德蘭陛下 還下著雨 您這樣出來對身體不好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請快回屋內
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.47,0:01:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 瑟爾蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.69,0:01:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是朕請導師過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪能不親自迎接呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 導師 走這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:46.52,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}悲しみに囚われた魂達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:46.52,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}為悲傷所困的靈魂們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:56.30,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}終わらない憎しみが叫びだす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:56.30,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}因無盡的憎恨而呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:02:01.61,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}迷いの森を抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:02:01.61,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}穿過迷惘的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.92,0:02:05.29,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}世界照らしに行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.92,0:02:05.29,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我們將去照亮世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.61,0:02:10.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}絶望抱きしめるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.61,0:02:10.68,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}會去擁抱絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:15.40,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}諦めていない証
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:15.40,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}說明還未放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:21.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}孤独超えたら信じあえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:21.28,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}當我們跨越孤獨便可互相信任
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:24.15,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}絆離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:24.15,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}不要放開這份情感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:28.97,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}希望という眩しい重さに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:28.97,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}希望炫目而又沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:34.67,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}負けない情熱この手にある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:34.67,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}手中握有不被壓倒的熱誠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:41.23,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}想い  光へ  何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:41.23,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}思念化作光芒 無論多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:45.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}命尽き果てるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:45.17,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}直至生命耗盡
